title: Indian on the Tootsie Roll Wrapper
subtitle: Can a Tootsie Pop wrapper picturing an Indian shooting an arrow at a star be redeemed with Tootsie Roll Industries for a free bag of candy?
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: A Tootsie Pop wrapper with a picture of an Indian shooting an arrow at a star on it can be redeemed with Tootsie Roll Industries for a free bag of candy.
